subject: Absolutely love it!
feedback: The new Motorola phone is fantastic. The camera quality is superb and the battery life is amazing. Best purchase this year!

subject: Slow response time
feedback: I sent an email to support three days ago and still haven't heard back. Very frustrating experience.

subject: Double charged for my order!
feedback: I was charged twice for my order #12345. This is unacceptable! I need a refund immediately.

subject: Great phone, minor issue
feedback: The phone is great overall, but the fingerprint sensor can be a bit slow to respond sometimes. Otherwise, very happy.

subject: Question about warranty
feedback: Just wanted to know what the warranty covers. The process to find this info was not very clear on the website.

subject: Phone arrived with a scratch
feedback: My brand new phone came out of the box with a noticeable scratch on the screen. Very disappointed with quality control.

subject: Exceeded my expectations
feedback: The performance is so smooth and the display is beautiful. Motorola has really stepped up its game.

subject: Support agent was very helpful
feedback: I had an issue with my account and the support agent (Sarah) was very patient and resolved it quickly. Great service!

subject: Payment failed multiple times
feedback: I tried to purchase the phone but my payment kept failing. The error message was not helpful. It was just an average experience.

subject: Battery drains too fast
feedback: The battery life is not as advertised. I have to charge it twice a day with normal use. Not happy about this.

subject: Feature request for camera app
feedback: It would be great if you could add a pro mode to the camera app. The current options are a bit basic, but the hardware is great.

subject: Inquiry about corporate discounts
feedback: Your team responded very quickly to my inquiry about bulk orders. Very professional and helpful.

subject: Delivery was delayed by a week
feedback: My delivery was supposed to arrive last Tuesday and it only came today. The tracking information was not updated.

subject: Refund processed quickly
feedback: I had to return an accessory and the refund was processed the very next day. I appreciate the efficiency.

subject: The phone is just okay
feedback: It does the job, but there's nothing special about it. It feels like any other phone in this price range. It's okay.

subject: Best phone I've ever owned!
feedback: From the design to the software, everything is perfect. I'm recommending it to all my friends.

subject: Chatbot is useless
feedback: The chatbot on the website couldn't understand my simple question and I had to wait 20 minutes to talk to a human.

subject: Billing error fixed instantly
feedback: I noticed an error on my bill, contacted support, and they fixed it within 5 minutes. Amazing service!

subject: Good value for the price
feedback: For what you pay, this phone is a great deal. It has features that are usually found in more expensive models.

subject: Website navigation is confusing
feedback: I had a hard time finding the 'contact us' page. It should be more prominent on the homepage.
